<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.1.4">
<l>veṉṟiyē vēṇṭi vīḻporuṭ kiraṅki</l>
<l>vēṟkaṇār kalaviyē karuti</l>
<l>niṉṟavā nillā neñciṉai yuṭaiyē</l>
<l>ṉeṉceykēṉ neṭuvicum paṇavum</l>
<l>paṉṟiyā yaṉṟu pārakaṅ kīṇṭa</l>
<l>pāḻiyā ṉāḻiyā ṉaruḷē</l>
<l>naṉṟunā ṉuyya nāṉkaṇṭu koṇṭēṉ</l>
<l>nārā yaṇāveṉṉum nāmam.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I had a heart which was unsteady, the way it kept wanting success,</l>
<l>Wailing for diminished wealth, thinking only of the embraces</l>
<l rend="indent">of lance-eyed ladies; what could I do?</l>
<l>By the grace of the discus-bearer, the strong one</l>
<l rend="indent">who split the broad earth that day as a boar</l>
<l rend="indent">which approached high heaven,</l>
<l>To be saved well, I discovered for myself the name which is pronounced,</l>
<l rend="indent">“Nārāyaṇā!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
